_sText:
About The Map: The maps theme is River/Surf
This map contains: A really simple and easy jail to get out of, Smooth surf ramps, This map is for people who enjoy fast surfing, Contains secret spots and teleports (Good Luck trying to find them).

I am not the original creator of this map. I have did a lot of modifications and added my own designs. I have taken the surf ramps from greatriver xdream. 

Credits: I am really grateful that someone out there created such a great map. I myself love greatriver and remakes of it.

And credit to black, since I took his surf ramps.
